{"tid":627444,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"星島日報:C朗冷血：祖記投訴無理","createTime":"2018-04-13T03:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T06:23:50.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d3fc45a27ac2b9daaa31d3bdc71242628bb77a20","tid":627444,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:40:41.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/c%E6%9C%97%E5%86%B7%E8%A1%80-%E7%A5%96%E8%A8%98%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E7%84%A1%E7%90%86-221121569--spt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fsports%2Fc%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%2586%25B7%25E8%25A1%2580-%25E7%25A5%2596%25E8%25A8%2598%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2590%2586-221121569--spt.html&d=0oCxB4PKUF1ZroO7ywWN2J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=0d1b1b87\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/sports/c%E6%9C%97%E5%86%B7%E8%A1%80-%E7%A5%96%E8%A8%98%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E7%84%A1%E7%90%86-221121569--spt.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】因一個爭議性十二碼，祖雲達斯門將保方再一次無緣歐聯錦標。操刀的皇家馬德里射手C朗拿度不但沒同理心，還批評保方等投訴無理。同時，他今仗射入關鍵十二碼後，成為歐聯史上首位連續十一仗士哥的球員。<br />\n<br />\n　　外界普遍對保方的遭遇深感同情，C朗卻落井下石：「我不明白他們為甚麼要投訴？若沒有犯規，盧卡斯華斯基斯已經將球射入網。今仗貝拿迪亞等祖雲達斯球員多次從後侵犯我們。」或許自知禍從口出，他賽後在球員通道跟保方擁抱，以表同情。<br />\n<br />\n　　個人層面，C朗繼續創紀錄，在今仗個人第一百五十場歐聯射入關鍵十二碼，自上季決賽至今連續十一場士哥改寫歷史；一季入十五或以上已是歐聯紀錄，他更連續三季達此指標。他各戰綫亦連續十一場為皇馬士哥，只差一場便平個人紀錄。"},{"pid":"1e88e7def1d2a579589a5c8e56479135f24e2d1b","tid":627444,"uid":7790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"當疤狗成為體育記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6676fbcaa9f687a27a92859751f29d1835605b2","tid":627444,"uid":52876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc7676170ca7349f49cb3ee1115534c19cb6e43","tid":627444,"uid":49724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"疤狗定蛆狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439e3e7cc0161d259746c479c39eb5d8354c6c9d","tid":627444,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:23:50.000Z","msg":"反牙朗已經做緊記者<br />\n反小花既仲讀緊書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}